      • getFromPhysicalBusId

        java.lang.String getFromPhysicalBusId()
        get from Bus id, the physical bus connected to the branch at the from side. The method should be only used to deal with the consolidated network situation.

      • getToPhysicalBusId

        java.lang.String getToPhysicalBusId()
